snippet.title: Samurai Sudoku - easy (solved using Excel VBA)
snippet.description: Solve an easy Samurai Sudoku puzzle using VBA for MS Excel. No guessing required. Only one possibilty as each square is solved in logical order testing numbers from 1 to 9.
